article.headline: Princeton 67, Columbia 52
article.story: NEW YORK -- Dan Mavraides scored 22 points to help Princeton beat Columbia 67-52 on Saturday night in the Ivy League. Mavraides was 7 of 9 from the field for the Tigers (17-8, 8-3). Kareem Maddox added 17 points and 10 rebounds, and Davis Douglas had 14 points. Niko Scott led Columbia (10-16, 4-8) with 12 points, and Kevin Bulger had 11.
